OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FRoyals and politicians have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to "remarkable" former MI6
OL,9,Fchief Sir Alex Younger, who has died
OL,10,Faged 62.
OL,12,FSir Alex led the Secret Intelligence
OL,13,FService, the UK's foreign intelligence
OL,14,Fservice, between 2014 and 2020. He
OL,15,Fdied on Tuesday, June 2, after being
OL,16,Ftreated for cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
