OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FKeir Starmer praised Sir Alex's
OL,8,F"utmost dedication" to protecting the
OL,9,Fcountry. David Cameron, who was prime
OL,10,Fminister when Sir Alex was head of the
OL,11,Fsecret service, said Britain owed the
OL,12,Fformer spy "an enormous debt of
OL,13,Fgratitude".
OL,15,FThe Prince of Wales said Sir Alex
OL,16,Fembodied "the very best of what the
OL,17,FSecret Intelligence Service stands
OL,18,Ffor".
OL,20,FCameron said the news of Sir Alex's
OL,21,Fdeath had "knocked me for six".
