OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FPaying tribute to Sir Alex, Cameron
OL,8,Fsaid: "I had the privilege to continue
OL,9,Fworking with Alex and to remain good
OL,10,Ffriends after we both left office; I
OL,11,Fwill miss him dreadfully. He was a
OL,12,Fremarkable man ` tremendously
OL,13,Fknowledgeable and insightful, but also
OL,14,Fsuch fantastic company and fun to be
OL,15,Fwith.
OL,17,F"Kind, thoughtful; a good man in every
OL,18,Fsense. At a time when our world is
OL,19,Fmore confrontational, volatile and,
OL,20,Ffrankly, dangerous, his expertise and
OL,21,Fgreat wisdom will be deeply missed."
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
