OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,F"Due to the nature of their work, few
OL,8,Ffully understand the service and
OL,9,Fsacrifice made by those working in our
OL,10,Fintelligence and security services `
OL,11,Fbut, be in no doubt, Alex made our
OL,12,Fcountry a safer place and we all owe
OL,13,Fhim an enormous debt of gratitude for
OL,14,Fthat," Cameron continued.
OL,16,FWilliam, in a personal message posted
OL,17,Fon Kensington Palace's social media,
OL,18,Fpraised Sir Alex for his "integrity,
OL,19,Fcourage, and an unwavering commitment
OL,20,Fto protecting this country and its
OL,21,Fpeople".
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@ZOU}D@GO]
