OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FStarmer said he was "saddened" to hear
OL,8,Fof Sir Alex's death.
OL,10,F"Sir Alex Younger led an exemplary
OL,11,Flife and career, ultimately serving as
OL,12,Fchief of the Secret Intelligence
OL,13,FService from 2014 to 2020.
OL,15,F"He will be remembered by the many
OL,16,Fministers, colleagues, friends, and
OL,17,Ffamily for his utmost dedication to
OL,18,FBritish public life and protecting our
OL,19,Fnation. My thoughts are with his
OL,20,Ffamily at this difficult time."
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
