OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,8,Fshe was " deeply saddened" by Sir
OL,9,FAlex's death and said the UK owes him
OL,10,Fan "enormous debt of gratitude".
OL,12,F"His dedication, integrity and
OL,13,Foutstanding leadership as chief of MI6
OL,14,Fkept us all safe," she said.
OL,16,FCooper added: "I would like to extend
OL,17,Four deepest sympathies to his family
OL,18,Fand his friends at this incredibly
OL,19,Fdifficult time."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@OOU{D@PO]
