OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FBlaise Metreweli, the current chief of
OL,13,FMI6, said: "It is with immense sadness
OL,14,Fthat I am sharing the news that former
OL,15,FMI6 chief Sir Alex Younger died today
OL,16,Fafter fighting cancer for some time.
OL,17,FAlex embodied my service's values of
OL,18,Fintegrity, courage, creativity and
OL,19,Frespect.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
