OL,3,CRoyals and politicians pay tribute to
OL,4,C'remarkable' former MI6 boss Alex
OL,5,CYounger
OL,7,F"We remember Alex's deep commitment to
OL,8,Fpublic service and the security of the
OL,9,FUK. He made a lasting and distinctive
OL,10,Fcontribution to our country and indeed
OL,11,Fto global security. Today my thoughts
OL,12,Fand those of the whole of MI6 are with
OL,13,FAlex's loved ones."
